These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, techno, jazz
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, french, malaysian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, tennis, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4
2. the french is on the left of the mexican##1
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the french is in an even position##4
5. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz       | disco     | techno    |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | french          | mexican   |
| Sport         | handball | snowboarding | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, pomegranate, mango
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, puzzles, drawing
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, pilot, project-manager
1. the project-manager is the person eating mango##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
4. the pilot is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
5. the project-manager is in an even position##4
6. the project-manager is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Food    | pear     | mango  | pomegranate  |
| Hobby   | drawing | puzzles | writing    |
| Job     | bartender      | project-manager    | pilot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-3::.
There 3 different types of food: peas, lettuce, avocado
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, disco, jazz
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, basketball, rugby
1. the person who's sport is swimming is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is rugby is the person eating peas##1
3. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of punk##1
4. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating peas##1
5. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |
| Food          | peas         | avocado     | lettuce   |
| Music-Genre   | disco       | punk     | jazz |
| Sport         | rugby | swimming | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, water, juice
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, musician, analyst
3 different pets are kept: horse, goat, frog
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the lawyer is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
5. the analyst is on the far left or far right##3
6. the musician is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |       3       |
| Beverage   | tea | juice  | water |
| Job        | analyst | musician  | lawyer |
| Pet        | horse | goat | frog         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: zombie, family, scientific
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, french, british
3 different pets are kept: ferret, hedgehog, goldfish
1. the nigerian is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
2. the french is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
6. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | zombie  | family  |
| Nationality   | french  | nigerian | british |
| Pet           | hedgehog  | goldfish    | ferret    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, almond-milk
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, sudoku, photography
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, trike, skateboard
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person driving the skateboard and the person who's hobby is photography##2
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk  | hot-chocolate  | tea        |
| Hobby       | photography | sudoku | drawing |
| Transport   | jet-ski    | trike   | skateboard   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, horror, drama
3 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret, hedgehog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, rugby
1. the person watching horror movies is between the owner of the lizard and the person watching drama movies##2
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | action | horror        | drama |
| Pet           | lizard   | ferret      | hedgehog     |
| Sport         | rugby | biathlon | badminton    |

