.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: lemon, eggplant, spinach
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, paramedic, manager
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, sailing, handball
1. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is between the manager and the person eating spinach##2
3. the paramedic is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person eating spinach is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is handball is the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3       |
| Food    | lemon   | eggplant | spinach       |
| Job     | manager  | bartender  | paramedic |
| Sport   | sailing | badminton  | handball       |

