.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, gardening, cooking
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, turkish, argentine
3 different pets are kept: lizard, turtle, dog
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the mexican is in an odd position##4
3. the turkish is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
4. the mexican is on the right of the turkish##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is between the owner of the lizard and the person who's hobby is gardening##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | gardening | writing | cooking |
| Nationality   | argentine       | turkish  | mexican     |
| Pet           | turtle     | dog     | lizard          |

