.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, mechanic, police-officer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, musical, disaster
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, argentine, canadian
1. the mechanic is on the far right##1
2. the person watching musical movies is the person watching musical movies##1
3. the japanese is on the left or right of the canadian##3
4. the doctor is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the canadian is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3    |
| Job           | police-officer | doctor        | mechanic   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | disaster | adventure    |
| Nationality   | canadian         | japanese      | argentine |

