.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, journalist, software-developer
3 different pets are kept: hamster, lizard, rat
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, motorbike, jet-ski
1. the software-developer is the owner of the hamster##1
2. the nurse is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the journalist is on the left of the nurse##1
5. the person driving the train is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2      |    3    |
| Job         | software-developer | journalist      | nurse  |
| Pet         | hamster         | rat      | lizard    |
| Transport   | train         | jet-ski | motorbike |

