.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-12::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, magic-tricks, baking
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, manager, firefighter
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, disaster, spy
1. the manager is the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the paramedic is in an even position##4
3. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
5. the firefighter is the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |      3       |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks        | rock-climbing  | baking      |
| Job           | firefighter | paramedic | manager |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster        | epic   | spy  |

