.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, water
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, rugby, skiing
The people use 3 different means of transport: ship, trike, taxi
1. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
3. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage    | lemonade        | juice | water     |
| Sport       | climbing | rugby          | skiing |
| Transport   | trike     | taxi          | ship       |

