.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-14::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, pumpkin, cherry
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, journalist, electrician
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, r&b, jazz
1. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
2. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
3. the electrician is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
4. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
5. the journalist is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Food          | asparagus | pumpkin | cherry |
| Job           | paramedic | electrician   | journalist  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | dubstep   | jazz        |

