.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, western, satire
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, reggae, folk
3 different pets are kept: fish, cat, horse
1. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the fan of blues is the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
4. the person watching western movies is the fan of reggae##1
5. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | satire | disaster |
| Music-Genre   | reggae        | blues         | folk |
| Pet           | fish | horse         | cat   |

