1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3
3. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |
| Beverage    | lemonade | cola      | 7up     |
| Pet         | dog  | mouse | frog        |
| Transport   | trike | airplane    | taxi |

