.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, reading, video-games
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, animation, horror
3 different pets are kept: rat, goat, hedgehog
1. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person watching animation movies##2
2. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching horror movies is the owner of the goat##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
7. the person watching disaster movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby         | video-games      | reading | singing |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | disaster      | horror    |
| Pet           | hedgehog      | rat        | goat       |

 